stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_compute_size: sampling_size = max(SAMPLES_PER_SLOT, custody_group_count)
    q_compute_size --> q_get_groups: groups = get_custody_groups(node_id, sampling_size)
    q_get_groups --> q_get_columns: columns = compute_columns_for_custody_group(group) for group in groups
    q_get_columns --> q_download: for each column in columns
    q_download --> q_check_retrieved: has next column
    q_download --> q_evaluate: no more columns
    q_check_retrieved --> q_download: column retrieved successfully
    q_check_retrieved --> q_fail: column retrieval failed
    q_evaluate --> [*]: sampling successful (all columns retrieved)
    q_fail --> [*]: sampling failed
